Vlocity Insurance Group Benefits Large Group Quoting

Before You Begin
Make sure the Quote record page is configured with all the options you need.
Determine what type of large group quote(s) you want to create.
Confirm that the product models you plan to quote are complete and up-to-date.
Confirm that the rating procedures for the product models you plan to quote are complete and up-to-date.

To learn about how to configure the quote UI with these settings, see Configure the Quote UI.
